    {
      "type": "text", "version": 2, "versionNonce": 653, "isDeleted": false, "id": "m_chain_detail",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "x": 1050, "y": 720, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 320, "height": 140, "seed": 653, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "M1 -> OnNetworkSpawn (initialization)\n     Fix: manual event fire for late-joiners\n\nM2 -> RPC validation layer (server-side)\n     Fix: add GameState guard to all day RPCs\n\nM3 -> Event subscription (cleanup phase)\n     Fix: subscribe CarriedItem to DayPhaseCleanup\n\nM4 -> Despawn lifecycle (server authority)\n     Fix: check and handle before NetworkObject despawn\n\nM5 -> Connection lifecycle (topology)\n     Fix: ConnectionManager detect host loss", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "M1 -> OnNetworkSpawn (initialization)\n     Fix: manual event fire for late-joiners\n\nM2 -> RPC validation layer (server-side)\n     Fix: add GameState guard to all day RPCs\n\nM3 -> Event subscription (cleanup phase)\n     Fix: subscribe CarriedItem to DayPhaseCleanup\n\nM4 -> Despawn lifecycle (server authority)\n     Fix: check and handle before NetworkObject despawn\n\nM5 -> Connection lifecycle (topology)\n     Fix: ConnectionManager detect host loss", "lineHeight": 1.25
